{"tid":2491407,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【8.31 案】黎智英監禁8個月  楊森監禁8個月 緩刑1年 李卓人 監禁6個月","createTime":"2021-04-16T09:39:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T09:48:39.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ff7d3751ea976e244131d19b93171cc380f418a0","tid":2491407,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T09:39:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15087\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F15087&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLQEiaVT8aWta%2BTWQuzHxyy8%3D&h=2330ddb3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15087</a><br />\n<br />\n#西九龍法院第一庭 (暫代區院)<br />\n#胡雅文法官 #判刑 #英語聆訊 <br />\n👥黎智英,楊森,李卓人 #0831灣仔<br />\n 🛑黎智英因另案而還押4個月🛑<br />\n<br />\n控罪：明知而參與未經批准集結<br />\n3人被控於2019年8月31日，在香港明知而參與一個未經批准集結。<br />\n==================<br />\n在考慮公民抗命的議題時，法庭表示不會考慮各人背後的理念及政治立場(按：也可參考陳仲衡法官就傘運的判決)。<br />\n<br />\n法庭表示本案沒有量刑指引，但考慮到所有與案因素，2019年起的社運背景，並參考相關案例，包括張慧玲法官就周庭案的判詞，上訴法庭就黃之鋒案的判決，鐘嘉豪案等，指出本案亦需要阻嚇性，以警誡他人勿犯案，保護公眾等元素的判刑，在判刑時也要考慮其潛在風險，其引發的事件等(例：無視警方警告等)。而個人良好的背景不會在量刑考量時給予太大比重。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Freedom of expression&rdquo;及&rdquo;Break the law&rdquo;不是法庭認為合理的辯解。<br />\n<br />\n以下是判刑結果：(持續更新)<br />\n黎智英：<br />\n即時監禁8個月<br />\n<br />\n楊森：<br />\n即時監禁8個月，緩刑1年<br />\n<br />\n李卓人：<br />\n即時監禁6個月<br />\n<br />\n詳細內容希望大家閱讀其他報道。"},{"pid":"8651e34b06e75d86e3990acb70b1931511e61d13","tid":2491407,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T09:40:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dac341c11c007a33ed20761e1b2782d9fed48f4","tid":2491407,"uid":170949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T09:40:36.000Z","msg":"手土"},{"pid":"6314f60b50a152a40edcda67548b8f0c8deb34d5","tid":2491407,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T09:40:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7fabe25f5b6a43529679866ee62a4813e0085ff","tid":2491407,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T09:41:50.000Z","msg":"考慮到黎智英及李卓人涉及另案的判刑，但涉及相同控罪下，2項控罪的刑罰同期執行。"},{"pid":"1a5cd6c2e7fedfb8297e3057119dc2d865c149b5","tid":2491407,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T09:42:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以下是判刑結果：(持續更新)<br />\n黎智英：<br />\n即時監禁8個月<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n8個月算好彩啦<br />\n<br />\n佢知唔知其他手足付出幾多？"},{"pid":"1bf21c7c173e290168a7927a00ad208270036989","tid":2491407,"uid":90692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1a5cd6c2e7fedfb8297e3057119dc2d865c149b5","tid":2491407,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T09:42:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以下是判刑結果：(持續更新)<br />\n黎智英：<br />\n即時監禁8個月<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n8個月算好彩啦<br />\n<br />\n佢知唔知其他手足付出幾多？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T09:43:45.000Z","msg":"冇人話佢唔好彩，冇人話過其他人付出唔多，唔需要咁敏感"},{"pid":"86cf06aa6389dd01838017e98a14b224b116f6b3","tid":2491407,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7fabe25f5b6a43529679866ee62a4813e0085ff","tid":2491407,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T09:41:50.000Z","msg":"考慮到黎智英及李卓人涉及另案的判刑，但涉及相同控罪下，2項控罪的刑罰同期執行。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T09:43:48.000Z","msg":"*法庭考慮到黎智英及李卓人涉及另案的判刑，但涉及相同控罪下，2個月的刑罰分期執行<br />\n<br />\nComplicated sentence, the gist of which is (I believe) Jimmy Lai and Lee Cheuk-yan get two months for the 8/31 protest added to their 8/18 sentences. Yeung Sum's sentence was suspended.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/austinramzy/status/1382993009017450500\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Faustinramzy%2Fstatus%2F1382993009017450500&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLQEiaVT8aWta%2BTWQuzHxyy8%3D&h=87e9270c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Faustinramzy%2Fstatus%2F1382993009017450500&h=d7b69ce2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/austinramzy/status/1382993009017450500</a>"},{"pid":"de1e271bf6b62446d57b848ddf4dad55159d54fe","tid":2491407,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T09:44:46.000Z","msg":"壹傳媒創辦人黎智英、職工盟秘書長李卓人及民主黨前主席楊森，前年8月31日參與在港島舉行的「為香港罪人祈禱大遊行」，3人在案件開審前承認同一項「明知而參與未經批准集結罪」，今（16日）判刑。黎智英判即時監禁8個月；楊森判監禁8個月、緩刑12個月；李卓人判即時監禁6個月。<br />\n<br />\n法庭考慮本案與818案事發日期相近，黎智英及李卓人於本案的刑期，會與818案分期執行兩個月，意指兩人會因兩案共判囚14個月。"},{"pid":"06f939329334617565e195b4dfa490607efe67b1","tid":2491407,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T09:48:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbeef5ee36ecdf051b9725bd35835886f0200dc3","tid":2491407,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T09:48:39.000Z","msg":"法庭考慮到黎智英及李卓人涉及另案的判刑，但涉及相同控罪下，2個月的刑罰分期執行，即：<br />\n<br />\n黎智英共需服刑14個月 (8.18+8.31)<br />\n李卓人共需服刑14個月 (8.18+8.31)<br />\n<br />\n詳細內容希望大家閱讀其他報道。<br />\n<br />\n17:45此為最終版本"}]}